item.description:
@hmsp wrote:

[quote=“Mendorphins, post:2, topic:371438”]I’m not sure about the plugin error, but for the compiler error you going to have to go through the most recent code you was at and check you didn’t miss any opening or closing brackets.

100 errors is most common for this, it doesn’t actually mean you’ve got 100 errors.
I already checked for that but there arent any extra…
Also, use the code tags next time.[/quote]
Ive checked for them but i havent found any.

item.title: Help my server wont run!-.-
item.dc:creator: @Mendorphins Mendorphins
item.description:
@Mendorphins wrote:

I’m not sure about the plugin error, but for the compiler error you going to have to go through the most recent code you was at and check you didn’t miss any opening or closing brackets.

100 errors is most common for this, it doesn’t actually mean you’ve got 100 errors. If not, check for any quotation marks or semi-colons you may have missed. ({ } " "

Also, use the code tags next time.
